  "descriptionKo": "SIGMETRICS은 시스템 분야(Performance Evaluation)의 주요 국제 학회입니다. 최근 acceptance rate는 17.3% (2025년, 66/382편)입니다. 주요 연구 키워드: Routing, Optimization, Latency, Efficient, Distributed. 매년 6월 개최. CCF B등급, CORE A*, BK21 3점.",
  "descriptionEn": "SIGMETRICS is a leading international conference in Systems (Performance Evaluation). Recent acceptance rate: 17.3% (2025, 66/382 papers). Top research topics: Routing, Optimization, Latency, Efficient, Distributed. Typically held in June. CCF rank B, CORE A*."
